    /********************************************************************************
      BEGIN MACRO HEADER
     ********************************************************************************

        Name:       PM
        Author:     Chris Swenson
        Created:    2010-08-24

        Purpose:    Post a message using a pop-up

        Arguments:  Message to display

        Revisions
